                  <h4>Identity and Passport Services</h4>
                  <span class="role-date">June 2009 - August 2009</span>
                  <p>In my capacity as a project lead, I oversaw the design, engineering, and delivery of a VMware-based virtual hosting solution, which was utilised by several hundred developers and testers. To ensure consistency across configurations, I made extensive use of automation throughout the development and deployment process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="role">
                  <h4>UK&I Healthcare (Chennai) - Developer Cloud</h4>
                  <span class="role-date">June 2008 - June 2009</span>
                  <p>As the lead for design, engineering, and delivery, I oversaw the development and implementation of a VMware-based hosting solution, which enabled developers and testers to deliver virtual servers using the same Altiris modular automation packages that were used in production environments.</p>
                  <p>Additionally, I played a key role in recruiting the local operations team, and provided training and mentorship in order to ensure the ongoing maintenance and enhancement of the cloud hosting solution.</p>
