                  <p>As a member of a small Agile team, I played a significant role in delivering and operating solutions using Windows Internet Information Server, Windows DNS, and Squid proxies.</p>
                  <p>Additionally, I was a pivotal part of a team that designed, developed, and delivered a .NET web service for the 'Change of Address' application. Our team was one of the first to embrace the principles of the Agile manifesto.</p>
